: 1em;\">\r\n	<li>SDK is available to integrate for free.</li>\r\n	<li>iOS and Android platforms are supported.</li>\r\n	<li>The flow can be customised to fit into various scenarios (social media / messaging / photos).</li>\r\n	<li>The SDK user can brand the flow with own color palette.</li>\r\n	<li>Tunes can be purchased from iTunes and Amazon.</li>\r\n	<li>Vendors of the WOW SDK-based apps receive a share on each track the end user purchases.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1.3em; line-height: 1.6em; text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-850\" style=\"margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"http://ulab.vinova.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/WOW_logo_small.png\" alt=\"WOW_logo_small\" width=\"98\" height=\"30\" />SDK is coming soon to:</p>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-981\" src=\"http://ulab.vinova.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Products-WOW-platform2.png\" alt=\"Products-WOW-platform2\" width=\"500\" height=\"40\" />[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"554\" img_size=\"full\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" css=\".vc_custom_1440557870616{padding-bottom: 30% !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Products - WOW','','inherit','closed','closed','','671-revision-v1','','','2015-08-31 15:19:07','2015-08-31 15:19:07','',671,'http://ulab.vinova.sg/671-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1136,1,'2015-08-31 15:47:44','2015-08-31 15:47:44','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1127\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"shopit-text\"]\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 33px; font-weight: bold; text-shadow: 1px 1px #333;\">SNAP IT BUY IT</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"]\r\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][expose_video_background youtube=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=phTEu_CGpgk&amp;feature=youtu.be\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"content-moving\" css=\".vc_custom_1440582823298{background-