n, production, recruiting, marketing, and more.\r\nWe‘re looking for ambitious companies in every field, but we have a unique focus on Mobile, Digital Media, Consumer Electronics and Telemedicine.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>UNPARALLELED SUPPORT</h3>\r\nWe have more than 60 full-time employee’s focusing on Design, Production, Marketing, Business Development and Corporate Partnerships.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>ASIA, U.S. and EUROPE</h3>\r\nWe invest in Asia, U.S. and Europe. Headquartered in Singapore with production offices in Ho-Chi-Minh City and Warsaw. Soon opening affiliate offices in Hong Kong, London and Los Angeles.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>JUST THE BEGINNING</h3>\r\nWe started ULab in 2015 with a mission to help entrepreneurs make the world better.\r\n[/expose_featured_parallax][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Investment Intro','','inherit','closed','closed','','583-revision-v1','','','2015-11-15 07:44:39','2015-11-15 07:44:39','',583,'http://ulab.com/583-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1456,1,'2015-11-15 14:05:23','2015-11-15 14:05:23','','ProductSlides-Side-wow1120152','','inherit','open','closed','','productslides-side-wow1120152','','','2015-11-15 14:05:23','2015-11-15 14:05:23','',0,'http://ulab.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ProductSlides-Side-wow1120152.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1457,1,'2015-11-15 14:26:55','2015-11-15 14:26:55','','Products-WOW-1_03','','inherit','open','closed','','products-wow-1_03','','','2015-11-15 14:26:55','2015-11-15 14:26:55','',671,'http://ulab.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Products-WOW-1_03.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1458,1,'2015-11-15 14:27:45','2015-11-15 14:27:45','[vc_row el_class=\"noneDisplay\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1440720574136{margin-top: 20% !important;}\"]\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 3em; text-align: left; color: #fff; line-height: 1em; font-weight: bold; text-shadow: 1px 1px #DDD;\">Each memory</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 3em; text-align: left; color