as entrepreneurs and investors, and newer members who have brought additional skills onboard.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our team of dedicated country managers are integral to the way in which we help our portfolio companies. They have an unrivalled business-development network, and outstanding track record, with deep relationships and an ability to super-charge growth across the world via our teams in Singapore, Ho-Chi Minh, and Warsaw.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We want our portfolio companies to attack large and changing market opportunities.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','690-revision-v1','','','2015-11-16 06:54:34','2015-11-16 06:54:34','',690,'http://ulab.com/690-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1461,1,'2015-11-17 06:14:50','2015-11-17 06:14:50','[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1444376337844{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"1439\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"shopit-text\"]\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 30px; font-weight: bold; text-shadow: #333333 1px 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 33px;\">Anything\r\nAnywhere\r\nAnytime</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\r\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][expose_video_background youtube=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=phTEu_CGpgk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" fallback=\"1361\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"content-moving\" css=\".vc_custom_1441287067700{background-image: url(http://ulab.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/shutterstock_259971707.jpg?id=1144) !important;}\" el_class=\"noneDisplay\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6em\"][vc_video link=\"https://vimeo.com/137922271\"][vc_column_text]<a class=\"blueButton\" href=\"/pdf/ShopIt.pdf\" target=\"_blank